                <text>9.1%</text>
            </label>
            <label key="aa3380ea26df33b9d6e8df4f1c76d9c8">
                <text>The wind turbines that the town is considering for the wind farm:</text>
            </label>
            <label key="64d75b84d89d985bdcfc8871975972b8">
